    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "NEZ PIERCE. Idaho, Sept. 19.-\nThe force of teams and men on the\ngrading of the Nez Perez & Idaho\nrailway has been increased in the\nlast few days and it is expected to\ncomplete the grade next month,\nwhen tracklaying will begin The\nNez Perez line will connect with\nthe Grangeville extension of the\nNorthern Pacific at Vollmer, with\nwhich traffic arrangements have al\nready been made."
    }
